{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_hamoni_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_hamoni_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"孤独的舞者","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"阿赫茉妮遇到了一个了解她的过去的人，对方提出可以让她摆脱情报人员的身份，而她没有同意。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_hamoni_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["丽塔","洛西莉","报刊亭老板","阿赫茉妮","好奇的贵族","夸夸其谈的商人","面色和善的贵族","陌生的声音","严厉的军官","温和的军官"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"Dialog","id":3},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_school","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.7","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$calm_loop","key":"$calm_loop","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":9},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_229_1#6","fadetime":"1","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":11},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"好久不见，洛西莉。","id":12,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"......","id":13,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"洛西莉！","id":14,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#6"},{"type":"Dialog","id":15},{"type":"Character","id":16},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","fadetime":"1","id":17},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":18},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"——啊，亲爱的丽塔。","id":19,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"我们是不是很久没机会说上话了？真可惜呀，我们没能像以前一样，被分到同一间宿舍。","id":20,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"近卫学校的军事化训练，真是比我们之前想象的还要繁重，你说是不是？","id":21,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_229_1#5","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"......你那天，赶上入学考试了吗？","id":23,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#3","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"咳咳......怎么突然问这个？我当然赶上了，不然我怎么会在这里？","id":25,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_229_1#6","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"......没事。给，你的《军事科学概论》。上面的批注和笔记很有用，多谢了。","id":27,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"考试当天早上我准备还给你，但是没等到你。我一直有点担心。","id":28,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"一起去吃晚饭吗？我们可以顺带聊聊天，你替我选选休息日穿的长裙。","id":29,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"不了，我正要赶去斯蒂芬妮举办的舞会呢。","id":31,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_229_1#4","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"你说那位莱塔尼亚伯爵的女儿？","id":33,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_229_1#5","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"我听说她的确有一些人脉，商人要寻找门路，音乐家和剧作家要找人引荐，先进入她的交际圈不会有错。","id":35,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"上次碰到你的时候，你是要去那位集团军参谋的外孙女主持的宴会，那样的军事家族总是需要培养一些亲信。","id":36,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"但是，那应该都跟你的志向没什么关系。过去你是不喜欢那些吵闹的社交活动的。","id":37,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"别这么说，丽塔。我就不能只是喜欢跳舞吗？","id":39,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_229_1#2","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"......好。","id":41,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"那等你下次有空闲时间，我们再聊吧。","id":42,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":43},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"别这么板着脸呀。","id":44,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"只是到了新环境，我们都需要一点时间来找到自己的节奏，不是吗？","id":45,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"（哼唱）......就像舞步的节奏。可惜，我多么希望你能陪我一起呀。","id":46,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_229_1#5","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"......洛西莉，你还记得我们为什么要努力考入皇家近卫学校吗？","id":48,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"当然啦，为了成为优秀的军人。","id":50,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_229_1#6","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"嗯。不是军官，不是军事贵族，是军人。我不想当一个像父亲那样只知道明哲保身的斯卡曼德罗斯。","id":52,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"而你想像我们的老师那样，做一个能坚定捍卫秩序的军人。","id":53,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_229_1#5","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"我的意思是......你如果有什么心事，可以跟我说。","id":55,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"丽塔","text":"老师过世之后，我们还没有去她的墓前看望过吧。","id":56,"figure":"avg_npc_229_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"......啊，真不好意思，我得走了，丽塔。","id":58,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"StopMusic","fadetime":"2","id":59},{"type":"dialog","id":60},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":61},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":62},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":63},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":64},{"type":"Background","image":"25_mini02_victoria_street_n","screenadapt":"coverall","id":65},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":66},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"$m_dia_street_loop","volume":"0.4","id":67,"musicid":1},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":68},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":69},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"报纸上是这么写的，“伦蒂尼姆及卡兹戴尔经济文化交流协会”。","id":71,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"不知道背后是哪位大公爵，找来那么一大队萨卡兹雇佣兵，作为自己放在伦蒂尼姆城内的棋子。","id":72,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"我可不这么想。","id":74,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"哎，别说别说。您要是知道什么内幕，也千万别跟我说。","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"哎呀，哪位大公爵最有可能掌控维多利亚，贵族之间对狮王后裔的下落有什么传言，有几座城市可能会爆发动乱......你都不好奇一下吗？","id":78,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"知道这种事，对我有什么好处呢？我连您是哪位市议员的家庭教师都不愿意知道。","id":80,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"不过，您家庭教师的身份，应该也是过去式了。","id":81,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":82},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"是呀，我昨天刚刚结束最后一次课程。","id":83,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"那位年幼的公子已经掌握了足够多的知识，当然也用不上我了。","id":84,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"哈哈......是您从他们那里打探到的消息足够多了吧。","id":86,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"你是说，多到我的上级决定自己负责这一带的事务，为他的荣誉墙再增添几枚勋章？","id":88,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1","id":89},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"咳、咳咳......我可不敢随便议论别人。","id":90,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"唉，您应该准备一些手段，避免这样被抢功。","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"这样的事情总会发生，有什么好在意的呢？","id":93,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"好啦，来一份时尚杂志。","id":94,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"好。","id":96,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":97},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$book_close","volume":"1","id":98},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"今后不管是哪位来，只要拿着您的这种特制硬币，就能买到这份杂志，我没弄错吧？","id":100,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":101},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"放心，牵线搭桥的工作我都已经做好了，你不会犯错的。","id":102,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"而且，你什么都不知情，就算有人找到你，也不能对你做什么。","id":103,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"你平静的生活不会被影响，只会得到我们承诺的报酬。","id":104,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"嘿嘿，您是了解我的。","id":106,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"多亏了这笔收入，我的孩子能上更好的学校了，他们会成为真正的绅士。","id":107,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"报刊亭老板","text":"对了，您花了多长时间，才磨掉自己身上军人的英气？我认识的那些军官，哪怕脱下制服，我也能分辨出来，您却不一样。","id":108,"figure":"avg_npc_417_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":109},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"军人？","id":110,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":111},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"......虽然我是军方的人，但我从来没有说过，我当过军人呀。","id":112,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"好啦，还有人邀请我赴宴，我该走了。","id":113,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"dialog","id":114},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":115},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":116},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":117},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":118},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":119},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"哪怕将来的某一天，邻近的城市地块坍塌，或者圣王会西部大堂血流成河，自己也可以置身事外，维持自己一贯的生活......","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"体面优雅的聪明人，我已经看厌了。","id":122,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"那么，让我看看......我的好线人会给我带来什么样的消息呢？","id":124,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":125},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","volume":"1","id":126},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":127},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":128},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"这封信......","id":130,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"......信被人调换过？里面夹了一张便条。","id":131,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"“......我知道你的身份，但我并非维多利亚的敌人。”","id":132,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"哎呀，这句话可证明不了你究竟是有意协助，还是想将我抓住。","id":134,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"所有人都喜欢说，自己是“为了维多利亚”。","id":135,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"当年无论是吊死狮王的人，还是坚定捍卫王室的人，可都同样觉得自己是在捍卫维多利亚呀。","id":136,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"要是各位努力的方向一致，也就不需要我这样刺探情报的人了。","id":137,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"或许，今晚在宴会上，我还要多传出去一条信息，弄清楚这位神秘人士究竟有什么意图。","id":138,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"dialog","id":139},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":140},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":141},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":142},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_manorgarden","screenadapt":"coverall","id":143},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":144},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":145},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_177","name2":"avg_npc_176","fadetime":"1","id":146},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":147},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_177","name2":"avg_npc_176","focus":"1","id":148},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"好奇的贵族","text":"你听说了吗？市议会的那些老顽固里总算有两个松口了，愿意再造一批蒸汽战车，同时出台法令，放宽对工厂主的限制。","id":149,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_177","name2":"avg_npc_176","focus":"2","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的商人","text":"哈哈，我们花在他们身上的金币至少没浪费。","id":151,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的商人","text":"越是上年纪的那些家伙，越是不敢表态。军队增添武备是常事，可是他们就害怕被人问：这是谁的军队？要去打谁？","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的商人","text":"自从没了狮王，这些问题就越来越不好回答了。","id":153,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_177","name2":"avg_npc_176","focus":"1","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"好奇的贵族","text":"那可不是，上个月病死在床上的那位老议员，你还记得吗？","id":155,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"好奇的贵族","text":"我听她的邻居说，那天晚上大家都隐约听见了惨叫声。谁敢说她实际上是不是病死的呢？","id":156,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_177","name2":"avg_npc_176","focus":"2","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的商人","text":"这就是老顽固们不肯放开手里权力的恶果。","id":158,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的商人","text":"走吧，我们去宴会厅里，请让我为您拿一杯酒。","id":159,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"Dialog","id":160},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":161},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","id":162},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":163},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","fadetime":"0.5","id":164},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"阴谋，贿赂，暗杀......没有什么新鲜事。","id":166,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#6","id":167},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"应该可以去那边的小阳台见见我的好伙伴了。","id":168,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#6"},{"type":"StopMusic","fadetime":"2","id":169},{"type":"dialog","id":170},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":171},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":172},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":173},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.4","id":175,"musicid":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":176},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":177},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_175","fadetime":"1","id":178},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"晚上好，阿赫茉妮小姐。","id":180,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"哎呀......","id":182,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_175","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"您现在有空吗？","id":184,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Dialog","id":185},{"type":"Character","id":186},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"1","id":187},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-100","fadetime":"0","block":"false","id":188},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"15","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":189},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_singleblunt","volume":"0.7","id":190},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"100","fadetime":"0.3","block":"false","id":191},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"不算太有空，如果您言行不够谨慎的话，我的源石技艺产生的水流会灌进您的气管，扼住您的喉咙。","id":193,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"2","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"您的反应真快。","id":195,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"1","id":196},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"您的气色不错，呼吸也没有变得急促。","id":197,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"2","id":198},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"您误会我了。我混入您的情报网留下一张字条，并不是打算威胁您什么。","id":199,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"1","id":200},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"那么，您找我是有什么事呢？","id":201,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"2","id":202},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"有位侯爵派我前来，向您传达善意。","id":203,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"1","id":204},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"......如果您想协助我们的工作，至少应该先带一些有效的情报来，不是吗？","id":205,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"2","id":206},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"不，我想为您提供一个新的去处。","id":207,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"您被迫成为情报人员，为已经腐朽的狮王军队效力，这实在是埋没了您的资质。","id":208,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"您也不应该再为自己数年前做错的一件小事受折磨，更何况，您当时完全不知情，这不能算是您的过错。","id":209,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"1","id":210},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"......他们为了隐瞒那桩丑闻，可是给了我不少好处。","id":211,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"您是不是知道得太多了？","id":212,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"StopMusic","fadetime":"3","id":213},{"type":"dialog","id":214},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":215},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":216},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":217},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.7","block":"true","id":218},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_warehouse","screenadapt":"coverall","id":219},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":220},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":221},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":222},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"老师，我回来了，信我已经带到了。","id":224,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"明天就是入学考试了，我还想请教您几个问题，主要是源石技艺测试方面......","id":225,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#2","id":226},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"......没有人在？","id":227,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":228},{"type":"Character","id":229},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$plot_intro","key":"$plot_loop","volume":"0.4","id":230,"musicid":3},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_knife","volume":"0.6","id":231},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_doorbreak","volume":"0.6","delay":"0.3","id":232},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":233},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"0.5","id":234},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$swordtsing1","volume":"0.6","delay":"0.3","id":235},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$swordtsing2","volume":"0.6","delay":"0.5","id":236},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":237},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#2","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"老师？您还好吗？","id":239,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"熟悉的撞击声，应该是老师用的那种军刀的声音......欸，难道是有人来抢劫？","id":241,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"老师那样身经百战的军人，处理几个匪徒应该绰绰有余。不过，正好我也可以测试一下自己的能力......","id":242,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Dialog","id":243},{"type":"Character","id":244},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":245},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陌生的声音","text":"......走私团伙已经全部击倒！进入仓库检查！","id":246},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#2","id":247},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"老师......霍里女士？","id":248,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":249},{"type":"Character","id":250},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","volume":"0.6","id":251},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陌生的声音","text":"这里还有残余同伙！","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陌生的声音","text":"放下武器！举起手来！","id":253},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#2","id":254},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"......你们是谁？","id":255,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#2"},{"type":"StopMusic","fadetime":"2","id":256},{"type":"dialog","id":257},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":258},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":259},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":260},{"type":"Background","image":"21_G2_opera_room","screenadapt":"coverall","id":261},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":262},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"$distressed_loop","volume":"0.4","id":263,"musicid":4},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":264},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_248","fadetime":"1","id":265},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":266},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"严厉的军官","text":"全都问清楚了？","id":267,"figure":"avg_npc_248"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_241","id":268},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"已经问过了，她是霍里的学生，年纪还小，对该团伙倒卖军方物资的事情一无所知。","id":269,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"她确实多次充当中间联络人的角色，帮霍里送信，但她并不知道自己转交的是什么，也没有怀疑过自己的老师。","id":270,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"霍里退伍后在一所贵族私立中学执教，近五年没有任何违规记录，很受学生尊敬。","id":271,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"那名学生本人回忆，霍里没有拉拢任何学生作为自己同伙的迹象，应该不必再对其他学生进行排查了。","id":272,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"我们已经控制她两天了，虽然只是普通问话，没有刻意施压，但根据观察到的细节来判断，她是十分诚实的。","id":273,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_248","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"严厉的军官","text":"好，让她进来吧，我们执行上面的安排。","id":275,"figure":"avg_npc_248"},{"type":"Dialog","id":276},{"type":"Character","id":277},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":278},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":279},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","fadetime":"1","id":280},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":281},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_248","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"严厉的军官","text":"你已经明白事件的前因后果了吗？","id":283,"figure":"avg_npc_248"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"老师犯了重罪，我在不知情的情况下成了帮凶......大致上应该是这样。","id":285,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#2","id":286},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"......请问，老师她最后......？","id":287,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_248","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"严厉的军官","text":"她拒绝配合，甚至率人和军方发生暴力冲突，只有死路一条。","id":289,"figure":"avg_npc_248"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"严厉的军官","text":"军方物资被倒卖的情况，我们已经追踪了一年多，霍里凭借自己过去在军队的人脉，成了倒卖链条中的关键人物，这一点不会有错。","id":290,"figure":"avg_npc_248"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"严厉的军官","text":"希望你不要对她有太多同情心。","id":291,"figure":"avg_npc_248"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":292},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"......嗯。","id":293,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_241","id":294},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"......她是个好老师吗？","id":295,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":296},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"她......","id":297,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"她是个坚定有力的战斗者，我很仰慕她展现出的力量。","id":298,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"比起礼仪课或是社交话术训练，似乎我从她那里学到的东西更有价值。","id":299,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"结果她做了这样的事情，然后以这种方式失败、倒下......","id":300,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"......有些出乎我的意料。仅此而已。","id":301,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#4","id":302},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"我尊敬的人，也不过如此而已呀。","id":303,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_241","id":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"对于你在这一事件中受到的冲击，我们表示理解。","id":305,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"请放心，我们不会追究你的所作所为，也不会将你视作她的同伙。","id":306,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"只是，我们希望你作为唯一知情的平民，务必对这一事件的真相保持沉默。","id":307,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"接下来，霍里将和另外两名参与倒卖的士兵一起，被记录为此次行动中军方的协助者。","id":308,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"你记住，他们是“在交战中英勇地牺牲”。她的死讯传到校园后，你对你的同学、老师或者其他人，都应该这么说。","id":309,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"他们还会被追授勋章。希望你能理解我们的良苦用心，为你尊敬的人维护身后的名誉，让她的死亡能体面一些。","id":310,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":311},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"......","id":312,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"嗯，我懂得该在什么事情上沉默。","id":313,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_241","id":314},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"很高兴我们能达成共识，你会得到一些好处。","id":315,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":316},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"好处？","id":317,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_241","id":318},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"你自述是为准备近卫学校入学考试而来找她。","id":319,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的军官","text":"你想进入皇家近卫学校，对吗？","id":320,"figure":"avg_npc_241"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#2","id":321},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛西莉","text":"我......","id":322,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#2"},{"type":"dialog","id":323},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":324},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":325},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"我还在乎吗？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":326},{"type":"subtitle","id":327},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":328},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_manorgarden","screenadapt":"coverall","id":329},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_175","id":330},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"2","amount":"0","block":"true","id":331},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":332},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":333},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"2","id":334},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"我不过恰好是当年军队内的知情者之一。","id":335,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"1","id":336},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"如果您是为了来与我叙旧，那您真是太客气了。","id":337,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"毕竟，那都已经是好几年前的事情了，连我自己都记不太清了。","id":338,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"2","id":339},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"正是您数年来的境遇令我同情，我不忍心看一名前途无量的年轻人得不到她应有的荣誉。","id":340,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"您应该能感觉到，您的人生在那场意外事件之后就已经不再受自己控制。","id":341,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"尽管进入了近卫学校，但尚未毕业，您就被迫改换身份隐姓埋名，从事情报工作，连真诚的人际关系都难以搭建。","id":342,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"好在，您同时可以说是十分幸运。眼下侯爵似乎对您的能力青睐有加，在我的引荐下，您可以接触到他，或许能凭努力成为他的亲信。","id":343,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"您既可以从情报人员这一身份中解脱，也能够获得更高的地位。","id":344,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"我这样说，能否取信于您？","id":345,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"1","id":346},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"......是呀，也不过是这些东西而已。","id":347,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"2","id":348},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"......您的意思是？","id":349,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_175","focus":"1","id":350},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"别放在心上，只是一句自言自语。","id":351,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"我倒是觉得，我们维持现在这样，我的法杖能抵着您喉咙的距离，显得更亲近一些。","id":352,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":353},{"type":"character","id":354},{"type":"Text","text":"说完，阿赫茉妮却抽回了法杖。","id":355},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":356},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"——请您离开吧。","id":357,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_175","id":358},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"女士，如果您是担心自己作为情报人员难以脱身才拒绝，请相信我们有足够的手段协助您。","id":359,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":360},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"看起来，您认为我一定要恨我的生活与我的命运才行。","id":361,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"您有一种不算少见的错觉，生活中处处埋藏着阴谋，许多小事件其实都有您这样的大人物在背后设计，是不是？","id":362,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_175","id":363},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"作为情报人员，您应该见过许多这样的情况。","id":364,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":365},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"是呀，已经见得有些厌倦了，甚至也做得有些厌倦了。","id":366,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"实际上，没有人胁迫我做情报工作。几位老师选中了我，我同意了，仅此而已。","id":367,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"你知道吗？如果我真的无力掌控自己的生活，那我现在就必须杀了你，免得你给我招来什么麻烦。","id":368,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#4","id":369},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"但我很喜欢你。","id":370,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_175","id":371},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"......","id":372,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":373},{"type":"StopMusic","fadetime":"3","id":374},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"好啦，我们应该都是来参加这场宴会的，是不是？","id":375,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":376},{"type":"Character","id":377},{"type":"Text","text":"阿赫茉妮轻巧地转身。","id":378},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$bar_intro","key":"$bar_loop","volume":"0.4","id":379,"musicid":5},{"type":"Text","text":"宴会厅里，乐队躬身准备开始演奏，通明的灯火透过落地窗，映亮她的轮廓。","id":380},{"type":"Dialog","id":381},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#6","fadetime":"0.5","id":382},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":383},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"（哼唱）","id":384,"figure":"avg_npc_228_1#6"},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","id":385},{"type":"Text","text":"她自顾自地抬手，转了个圈。","id":386},{"type":"Text","text":"在庭院里，她独自一人跳起轻快的舞步。","id":387},{"type":"Dialog","id":388},{"type":"Character","id":389},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":390},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_175","fadetime":"1","id":391},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":392},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面色和善的贵族","text":"您......要与谁共舞呢？","id":393,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"Character","id":394},{"type":"Text","text":"名叫阿赫茉妮的菲林没有回答。","id":395},{"type":"Dialog","id":396},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":397},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":398},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":399},{"type":"Character","id":400},{"type":"Image","id":401}],"characters":["丽塔","洛西莉","报刊亭老板","阿赫茉妮","好奇的贵族","夸夸其谈的商人","面色和善的贵族","陌生的声音","严厉的军官","温和的军官"]}